{
  "page": "A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 71",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(230, 230, 230)\">Daenerys X</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_dance_with_dragons\" title=\"A dance with dragons\"><img alt=\"ADanceWithDragons.jpg\" src=\"/images/7/79/ADanceWithDragons.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"337\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone_(hill)\" title=\"Dragonstone (hill)\">Dragonstone</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_sea\" title=\"Dothraki sea\">Dothraki sea</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n929 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(230, 230, 230)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_52\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 52\">Daenerys IX</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_70\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 70\">The Queen's Hand</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\">Daenerys X</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Epilogue\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Epilogue\">Epilogue</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_71&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:252px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Marc_Fishman_Drogon_flies_to_Dany.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c3/Marc_Fishman_Drogon_flies_to_Dany.jpg/250px-Marc_Fishman_Drogon_flies_to_Dany.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"302\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c3/Marc_Fishman_Drogon_flies_to_Dany.jpg/375px-Marc_Fishman_Drogon_flies_to_Dany.jpg 1.5x, /images/c/c3/Marc_Fishman_Drogon_flies_to_Dany.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Marc_Fishman_Drogon_flies_to_Dany.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Drogon\" title=\"Drogon\">Drogon</a> comes to Daenerys's call - by Marc Fishman ©</div></div></div>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys</a> is walking back south through the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_Sea\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dothraki Sea\">Dothraki Sea</a> towards <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>, following a small rivulet that she thinks will flow into the <a href=\"/index.php/Skahazadhan\" title=\"Skahazadhan\">Skahazadhan</a>. She has spent her time flying <a href=\"/index.php/Drogon\" title=\"Drogon\">Drogon</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup> but could not make him take her back. \n</p><p>Instead, they have been staying at his lair, a small cave in a hill she named <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone_(hill)\" title=\"Dragonstone (hill)\">Dragonstone</a> as a reference to <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">the place where she was born</a>. She gets sick on the way,<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;N 2&#93;</a></sup> and has a number of hallucinations as she lies in the grass, bleeding and dying. These include a vision of <a href=\"/index.php/Quaithe\" title=\"Quaithe\">Quaithe</a>, of <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a>, and of <a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a>, and seem to revolve around the idea of forgetting who she is. \n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:252px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Drogonsprey.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/61/Drogonsprey.JPG/250px-Drogonsprey.JPG\" width=\"250\" height=\"231\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/61/Drogonsprey.JPG/375px-Drogonsprey.JPG 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/61/Drogonsprey.JPG/500px-Drogonsprey.JPG 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Drogonsprey.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Dany and Drogon, by Ashley Hunter Rice ©</div></div></div>\n<p>Finally, a single <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> scout approaches her, but does not see her. The scout freezes as Drogon approaches, and then flees. Daenerys calls out for Drogon as he flies over, and mounts him. Drogon catches and devours a horse, and Dany joins him. This is how Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Jhaqo\" title=\"Jhaqo\">Jhaqo</a>, former <a href=\"/index.php/Ko\" title=\"Ko\">ko</a> of Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> accompanied by 50 of his warriors, finds her.\n</p>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> This article or section is a <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stub\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Stub\">stub</a>. You can help \"A Wiki Of Ice And Fire\" by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_71&amp;action=edit\">expanding it</a> and/or improving existing text.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span id=\"Character_List_appearing/mentioned\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_71&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List appearing/mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hizdahr_zo_Loraq\" title=\"Hizdahr zo Loraq\">Hizdahr zo Loraq</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Daario_Naharis\" title=\"Daario Naharis\">Daario Naharis</a></li>\n<li>Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jhogo\" title=\"Jhogo\">Jhogo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hero\" title=\"Hero\">Hero</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Groleo\" title=\"Groleo\">Groleo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaego\" title=\"Rhaego\">Rhaego</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Irri\" title=\"Irri\">Irri</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jhiqui\" title=\"Jhiqui\">Jhiqui</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Missandei\" title=\"Missandei\">Missandei</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Reznak_mo_Reznak\" title=\"Reznak mo Reznak\">Reznak mo Reznak</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Skahaz_mo_Kandaq\" title=\"Skahaz mo Kandaq\">Skahaz mo Kandaq</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Strong_Belwas\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Strong Belwas\">Strong Belwas</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Quaithe\" title=\"Quaithe\">Quaithe</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Magister_Illyrio\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Magister Illyrio\">Magister Illyrio</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aggo\" title=\"Aggo\">Aggo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rakharo\" title=\"Rakharo\">Rakharo</a></li>\n<li>Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Jhaqo\" title=\"Jhaqo\">Jhaqo</a></li>\n<li>Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Pono\" title=\"Pono\">Pono</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_71&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">After fleeing Meereen with him back in <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_51\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 51\">Chapter 51</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Some of the symptoms suggest that she may have caught the <a href=\"/index.php/Bloody_flux\" title=\"Bloody flux\">bloody flux</a>, but she is also bleeding and believes it is due to menstruation.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_71&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" clas